{"type": "article", "id": 4584, "title": "TUMI  2014 冬日假日系列新品", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-22T07:56:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135248POrsyNcYoepWDJvm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t美国箱包品牌 TUMI 近日带来 2014 冬日假日系列新品，设计团队以传统的许愿树为灵感，为这一系列的包袋赋予了丰富的图案与节日色彩，ALPHA 系列中的 ALPHA 2 Travel Satchel 旅行袋以及 Kingsville Deluxe Brief Pack® 背包展现了简洁的现代风格，而包括Nimes 小型旅行袋、TSA 锁扣，Key FOBs 锁匙扣及 Slim Luggage Tag 行李牌等旅行配件，也为旅途中如何保护随身携带的贵重财物提供了更多选择。 TUMI 2014 冬季假日系列将会陆续在各地门店发售，更多详情可以点击<a href=\"http://www.tumi.com/na/s/giftideas\"> </a><a href=\"http://www.tumi.com/na/s/giftideas\" target=\"_blank\">TUMI.com </a>查看。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135245I9251Ja0FeguZAMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135245WbmqxKaz46fRTCtB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135245nazi3SvTAIJyeXrk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135246ZmJU5ove0NCQHXpP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061352465HQUb8OVl6zvwEpj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135247pJwXH7bEvWjGeKBi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}